high_descs: Turn around and walk to the refrigerator on your right.
Remove a potato from the freezer.
Turn around and go to the sink in front of you.
Place the potato in the right sink, turn the water on, rinse the potato off, turn the water off and remove the potato from the sink.
Turn around and walk to the end of the kitchen island, then turn left and continue walking to the microwave across from you.
Place the potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean, cold potato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and take the potato out of the fridge.
Turn left and go to the sink with the potato.
Rinse the potato in the sink.
Turn all the way around and walk to the wall, then go left to the microwave.
Heat the potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Heat up the potato in the microwave.
